Output format
One table, written as parquet and/or a duckdb/sqlite table so Person B can query it with clean SQL. Ship alongside a small reconciliation report per source file: rows in / rows out, sum of amount_incl_vat ties to raw export, count of UNMAPPED accounts, count of null dates.

Schema owner: Person A. Changes require sign-off from B and C before merging.
